VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT APP_DEBUG\s*=\s*true|kernel\.debug\s*=\s*true|WP_DEBUG\s*,\s*true|ENVIRONMENT\s*=\s*[\'\"]development[\'\"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:release|production
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects framework/application debug mode enabled in deployable configuration.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Symfony Debug Mode Enabled.
